title: Class 1A First Round Playoff Preview
text:
Class 1A First Round Playoff Preview Luke Feddersen IowaPreps.com Editor 
Iowa Preps dives into the first round of the 2015 Class 1A playoffs. We take a look at each game, players to watch, and predicts the eventual winner. See what teams we feel have the abilities to move into the second round now! 
Game: Alburnett (7-2) at South Winneshiek (7-2)Top Overall Player: Carson Lensing, South Winneshiek Difference in the Game: Late season 
Who do we believe will win these first round matchups? What will be the biggest upsets? Who are the top players to watch? What other coverage am I missing by not subscribing? Football
